Package mdxmlconverter.relationship

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssociationConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert a PackagedElement to an UmlRelationship
    AssociationTypeConverter
    Class providing a static method which converts the aggregation attribute of a TemporaryAttribute to an UmlRelationshipType
    DependencyConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert a PackagedElement to a TemporaryRelationship with type UmlRelationshipType.DEPENDENCY
    GeneralizationConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert Generalizations to TemporaryRelationships with type UmlRelationshipType.GENERALIZATION
    InterfaceRealizationConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert InterfaceRealizations to TemporaryRelationships with type UmlRelationshipType.INTERFACEREALIZATION
    RelationshipConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert PackagedElements with type 'uml:Association' or 'uml:Usage' to TemporaryRelationships
    These TemporaryRelationships contain references to their client- and supplier elements which are later resolved
